Human pressure and biodiversity modify forest resilience after extreme multi-year droughts
                    Tianjing Wu1, Yanxu Liu 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-3571-19321, Liangzhi Chen 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-1021-821X2, Zheng Fu 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-7627-88243, Bojie Fu 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-9920-98024,5, Yan Li1, Xutong Wu 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0001-6124-04361, Jingyi Ding1, Changjia Li 
